title: A Day of the Baleada full of flavor!
content: Tegucigalpa, June 29, 2021.- Music, laughter and above all a lot of flavor. This is how Baleada Day was celebrated, where we shared with many Hondurans the delicious combinations they can make with their favorite snacks to enjoy their baleada. Without a doubt, a tradition as ours as Snacks Yummies.
